## Topic anchoring patterns

### Comments on a task entity

```typescript
const topic = await ModuleFE_Topic.upsert({
	anchor: {dbKey: 'tasks', id: taskId},
});
```

### Group chat (app-owned anchor)

Create a `DB_ChatRoom` entity in the app, then anchor:

```typescript
const topic = await ModuleFE_Topic.upsert({
	anchor: {dbKey: 'chat-rooms', id: chatRoomId},
});
```

### Finding existing topic for an entity

```typescript
const topic = ModuleFE_Topic.getTopicByAnchor({dbKey: 'tasks', id: taskId});
if (!topic) {
	// No conversation yet — create one
}
```

