## Naming conventions

| Artifact | Convention |
|----------|-----------|
| DB entity types | `DB_Topic`, `DB_Message` |
| DB defs | `DBDef_Topic`, `DBDef_Message` |
| Database def types | `DatabaseDef_Topic`, `DatabaseDef_Message` |
| Backend modules | `ModuleBE_TopicDB`, `ModuleBE_MessageDB`, `ModuleBE_MessagingApi` |
| Frontend modules | `ModuleFE_Topic`, `ModuleFE_Message` |
| Backend module pack | `ModulePackBE_Messaging` |
| Frontend module pack | `ModulePackFE_Messaging` |
| API type | `API_Messaging` |
| API def constant | `ApiDef_Messaging` |
| Permission scope | `PermissionScope_Messaging` |
| Access groups | `AccessGroup_MessagingRead`, `AccessGroup_MessagingWrite`, `AccessGroup_MessagingDelete`, `AccessGroup_MessagingAdmin` |
| Dispatcher interfaces | `OnTopicsUpdated`, `OnMessagesUpdated` |
| UI components | `Component_ChatPanel`, `Component_MessageList`, `Component_MessageInput`, `Component_MessageBubble`, `Component_ThreadPanel` |

